      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLYING ARTIE (1) comes here off a handy sixth over 530m at Angle Park in 30.58. Top run latest and looms as the one to beat. DAKOTA AVA (6) struggled for best form latest, finishing 5th (31.26) in a Grade 5 at Angle Park. Form here at this distance is strong including three wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Shapes as one to consider. HELD FOR RANSOM (3) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.22 beating Aileen's Shine. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. One of the prime contenders. FANTASTIC SPIKE (2) is in fine form and looks a good top-three chance again.",
